{"tid":760829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防止自殺會跟上時代　出App供求助","createTime":"2018-07-30T01:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T02:52:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60c114902bd4dec7b92a4e48b3a3413dc575674d","tid":760829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463050&d=bAgHhObGkLxSANTR6DeyJ5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=e3fb4d4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463050&h=cd69e241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463050</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月29日 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺會跟上時代　出App供求助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180729/large/29la7p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F29la7p11.jpg&h=4e2c9250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「低頭族」越來越多，情緒受困者求助模式亦改變。撒瑪利亞防止自殺會將加強網上輔導服務，包括在9月開學前開設跨平台應用程式「Chat窿」（圖），讓求助人可匿名、以短訊形式向專業輔導人員傾訴，該會總幹事曾展國希望程式成為求助者分享煩惱的「樹洞」，從而解除自殺危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致電熱線者多為中年人<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會現時設有的「真心話室」網上服務在2017年錄得2,695人次，當中最少逾一半為29歲或以下的年輕人，至於該會轄下的求助熱線，主要使用人次為中年人，29歲以下的人次只佔兩成左右，反映年輕一代偏向尋求網上服務。<br />\n<br />\n該會轄下自殺危機處理中心主任何永雄指，按以往經驗，除非青少年被迫接受輔導，例如在父母、社工要求下進行，否則青少年接受輔導的穩定性較成年人高，「因為成年人嘅自主性好高、會比較唔穩定，相反只要畀佢哋（青少年）感受到真係有人關心佢哋，會有較大機會解除危機」。防止自殺及情緒支援應用程式Chat窿將於8月22日正式推出。<br />\n<br />\n■記者周　婷  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n青少年尋死身亡個案連升3年　7歲童煩學業想自殺<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n警行動處長籲同袍潔身自愛"},{"pid":"0741f8e22e46c41c01be52025f85bd98855fb0a3","tid":760829,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自殺仲點會死之前仲咁得閒特登down個app嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7dc5d2244e15a8ef9e11257d97de51937764d2","tid":760829,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0741f8e22e46c41c01be52025f85bd98855fb0a3","tid":760829,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自殺仲點會死之前仲咁得閒特登down個app嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"想自殺既人係以為已經冇路行先會自殺"},{"pid":"fd57e4ad7093d4ac0cb02898bea5277506e5aee6","tid":760829,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0741f8e22e46c41c01be52025f85bd98855fb0a3","tid":760829,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自殺仲點會死之前仲咁得閒特登down個app嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"出APP目的係多條路比佢揀<br />\n多一分機會就多一線生機"},{"pid":"44fa20f1a1ab7bd9444547e2319b11e482a3ad5d","tid":760829,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd57e4ad7093d4ac0cb02898bea5277506e5aee6","tid":760829,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0741f8e22e46c41c01be52025f85bd98855fb0a3","tid":760829,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自殺仲點會死之前仲咁得閒特登down個app嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"出APP目的係多條路比佢揀<br />\n多一分機會就多一線生機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"因為以往只係出輔導熱線，但「無法接通、部分人士不肯開金口求助」為所詬病。<im